%% Diagram: Sync queue happy path with optimistic UI
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant Client as App + SW + IDB
    participant API as API

    U->>Client: edit
    Client->>Client: queue + optimistic UI
    Client-->>U: render
    Note over Client: online
    Client->>API: POST /sync (idempotent)
    alt 2xx
        API-->>Client: ack
        Client->>U: dismiss "saving"
    else 4xx
        API-->>Client: error
        Client->>U: surface conflict
    else 5xx
        Client-->>Client: retry on next sync
    end
